Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.87,0:23:48.13,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,150)}我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.87,0:23:48.13,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,520)}慢慢上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.83,0:24:03.13,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1100,340)}怎么办沉默了 我做学姐的一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.83,0:24:03.13,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(390,220)}嗯嗯 这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.83,0:24:03.13,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(205,275)}如果是少女漫画的情节
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.29,0:24:10.66,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,220)}诶
